DUBAI: Italian fashion label Tod’s tapped Australian-Lebanese model Jessica Kahawaty to star in a campaign for its Spring/Summer 2022 line. For the latest updates, follow us on Instagram @arabnews.lifestyle The actress, humanitarian and entrepreneur took to Instagram to share shots from the her time in Amalfi, Italy, as well as behind-the-scenes footage from the trip. “Grateful for these days of happiness, fresh air and beautiful nature,” she wrote to her 1.1 million followers.  A post shared by Jessica Kahawaty جيسيكا قهواتي (@jessicakahawaty) In the warm-toned pictures, taken by Italian photographer Gabriele D’Agostino, Kahawaty was seen sporting stylish cat-eye glasses with an oval-shaped white bag complete with the Tod’s logo. She also wore a colorful printed knit dress accessorized with a hot red bag with gold detailing. In other pictures, the Dubai-based star was seen wearing a long-sleeved fringed mini-dress, beige blazers and an orange jacket.